last_episode_to_air.overview: Despite Edda's embrace of a new dawn, the young God of Thunder cannot evade the predestined future that awaits.

name: Ragnarok
overview: A small Norwegian town experiencing warm winters and violent downpours seems to be headed for another Ragnarök -- unless someone intervenes in time.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In a Norwegian town poisoned by pollution and rattled by melting glaciers, the End Times feel all too real. It’ll take a legend to battle an old evil.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Mythical chaos looms as Magne looks for help in his continuing fight against giant foes and deals with an unmanageable brother with godlike powers.

tagline: This is where it all begins.

episodes.name: New Boy
episodes.overview: Returning to his family’s hometown, awkward teenager Magne discovers his strange new powers. Still, the hamlet's natural beauty cloaks dark secrets.

episodes.name: 541 Meters
episodes.overview: Magne and his classmates try to regroup after a tragic loss, while the police seem uninterested in getting to the truth. Gry stumbles on Vidar unmasked.

episodes.name: Jutulheim
episodes.overview: The break-in confirms what Magne suspects: He must take matters into his own hands. After tying up loose ends, the Jutuls put the teen to the test.

episodes.name: Ginnungagap
episodes.overview: A search for answers brings Magne back to a mysterious woman — and a meaningful mountain. Turid confronts Ran, and former BFFs Gry and Saxa get heated.

episodes.name: Atomic Number 48
episodes.overview: As Fjor holds Vidar back, Magne takes the blame, then tries a new tack. Threats abound, and the greatest is the explosive find that Isolde left behind.

episodes.name: Yes, We Love This Country
episodes.overview: While attempting to expose the truth, Magne gets another shock. Hope seems lost, but have the Jutuls underestimated their foe — and the power of good?

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: In a Norwegian town poisoned by pollution and rattled by melting glaciers, the End Times feel all too real. It’ll take a legend to battle an old evil.

episodes.name: Brothers in Arms
episodes.overview: A battle ends with a bang — and an ominous promise of violence. After visiting another realm, Magne hunts for allies while Vidar marshals his forces.

episodes.name: What Happened to the Nice, Old Lady?
episodes.overview: The truth hurts, and a fight for hearts and minds kicks off. Vidar gets under Magne's skin, Iman feels her power, and Laurits discovers his dark side.

episodes.name: Power to the People
episodes.overview: Edda rises: Magne confronts Ran, and Laurits proves a point. As protests gather momentum, a king walks again, and a master manipulator gets played.

episodes.name: God Is God, Though All Men Death Had Tasted
episodes.overview: A patriarch passes — and a strange new creature is born. Magne tries to change, Laurits lashes out and Fjor charts a new path. Saxa and Iman step up.

episodes.name: Know Yourself
episodes.overview: In a seismic shift, Magne rejects strength, Fjor makes a power grab and a circle closes ranks. Laurits learns the truth, and Iman reaches out to Ran.

episodes.name: All You Need Is Love
episodes.overview: Desperate times fire up Magne and his crew as they go on a risky mission. The Jutuls face an unforeseen enemy while a formidable ancient force awakens.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Mythical chaos looms as Magne looks for help in his continuing fight against giant foes and deals with an unmanageable brother with godlike powers.

episodes.name: War Is Over
episodes.overview: Bereft of his hammer, Magne continues to battle the Giants while complying with modern rules. But when he breaks a pact, the truce crumbles.

episodes.name: Till Death Do Us Part
episodes.overview: The Jutuls decide to play along with Magne's antics to make him more open to Saxa's plan. Feeling rejected by everyone, Laurits finds support in Jens.

episodes.name: Losing My Religion
episodes.overview: Under Saxa's spell, Magne continues to fall further from himself — a perfect distraction for Fjor to enact his vicious plan and set a dangerous trap.

episodes.name: My Precious
episodes.overview: More vulnerable than ever, Magne requires backup to face his relentless foes. An impossible ultimatum threatens Laurits' loved ones.

episodes.name: A Farewell to Arms
episodes.overview: As Magne's arrogance sows discord among his allies, the gods stand at a crossroads between forging lasting peace or fighting the impending battle.

episodes.name: Ragnarok
episodes.overview: Despite Edda's embrace of a new dawn, the young God of Thunder cannot evade the predestined future that awaits.
